---
import ProductLayout from '../../layouts/ProductLayout.astro';
---

<ProductLayout
	title="football-docs — Football data documentation for AI agents"
	description="Searchable football data provider documentation for AI coding agents. Like Context7 for football data."
	url="https://football-docs.withqwerty.com"
	accent="#1565C0"
	accentLight="#BBDEFB"
	favicon="/football-docs/favicon.png"
>
	<style>
		.hero {
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			gap: 2rem;
			margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		}

		.hero-icon {
			width: 80px;
			height: 80px;
			flex-shrink: 0;
		}

		.hero h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
			font-weight: 900;
			letter-spacing: -0.03em;
			line-height: 1.1;
		}

		.hero .tagline {
			color: var(--fg-muted);
			font-size: 1.1rem;
			margin-top: 0.25rem;
		}

		.pitch {
			font-size: 1.15rem;
			line-height: 1.7;
			max-width: 700px;
			margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
			color: var(--fg-muted);
		}

		.install-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
			gap: 0.75rem;
			margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		}

		.install-card {
			background: var(--card-bg);
			border: 2px solid var(--border);
			border-radius: var(--radius);
			padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
		}

		.install-card:hover { border-color: #1565C0; }

		.install-label {
			font-size: 0.75rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			text-transform: uppercase;
			letter-spacing: 0.08em;
			color: #1565C0;
			margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
		}

		.install-card code {
			display: block;
			font-size: 0.8rem;
			line-height: 1.6;
			color: var(--fg);
			background: none;
			padding: 0;
		}

		.section-title {
			font-size: 0.8rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			text-transform: uppercase;
			letter-spacing: 0.1em;
			color: #1565C0;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
			margin-top: 2.5rem;
		}

		.tools-row {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
			gap: 0.75rem;
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
		}

		.tool-card {
			background: var(--card-bg);
			border: 2px solid var(--border);
			border-radius: 12px;
			padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
		}

		.tool-card:hover { border-color: #1565C0; }

		.tool-name {
			font-family: var(--font-mono);
			font-size: 0.82rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			color: #1565C0;
		}

		.tool-desc {
			font-size: 0.82rem;
			color: var(--fg-muted);
			margin-top: 0.2rem;
		}

		.example-queries {
			list-style: none;
			display: flex;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
			gap: 0.5rem;
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
		}

		.example-queries li {
			background: var(--card-bg);
			border: 1px solid var(--border);
			border-radius: 20px;
			padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
			font-size: 0.85rem;
			color: var(--fg-muted);
			font-style: italic;
		}

		.providers-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr));
			gap: 0.5rem;
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
		}

		.provider-chip {
			background: var(--card-bg);
			border: 2px solid var(--border);
			border-radius: 10px;
			padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.provider-name {
			font-weight: 700;
			font-size: 0.9rem;
		}

		.provider-chunks {
			font-size: 0.75rem;
			color: var(--fg-muted);
		}

		.stat-row {
			display: flex;
			gap: 1rem;
			margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
		}

		.stat-card {
			flex: 1;
			min-width: 120px;
			background: #1565C0;
			color: white;
			border-radius: var(--radius);
			padding: 1.25rem;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.stat-number {
			font-size: 2rem;
			font-weight: 900;
			line-height: 1;
		}

		.stat-label {
			font-size: 0.8rem;
			opacity: 0.8;
			margin-top: 0.25rem;
		}

		.cta-banner {
			background: #1565C0;
			color: white;
			border-radius: var(--radius);
			padding: 2rem;
			text-align: center;
			margin-top: 2.5rem;
		}

		.cta-banner h2 {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
			font-weight: 900;
			margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		}

		.cta-banner p {
			opacity: 0.8;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
		}

		.cta-banner code {
			background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
			color: white;
			font-size: 0.9rem;
			padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
			border-radius: 6px;
		}

		.footer {
			margin-top: 2.5rem;
			padding-top: 1.5rem;
			border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
			color: var(--fg-muted);
			font-size: 0.85rem;
		}

		.footer a { text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }
	</style>

	<div class="hero">
		<img src="/football-docs/icon.svg" alt="football-docs" class="hero-icon" />
		<div>
			<h1>football-docs</h1>
			<div class="tagline">Like Context7 for football data</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<p class="pitch">
		Searchable documentation for 10+ football data providers, built for AI coding agents. Your agent looks up the real docs instead of guessing from training data. Works with any tool that supports MCP.
	</p>

	<div class="stat-row">
		<div class="stat-card">
			<div class="stat-number">640</div>
			<div class="stat-label">searchable chunks</div>
		</div>
		<div class="stat-card">
			<div class="stat-number">10+</div>
			<div class="stat-label">providers</div>
		</div>
		<div class="stat-card">
			<div class="stat-number">4</div>
			<div class="stat-label">MCP tools</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section-title">Install</div>

	<div class="install-grid">
		<div class="install-card">
			<div class="install-label">Claude Code</div>
			<code>claude mcp add football-docs -- npx -y football-docs</code>
		</div>
		<div class="install-card">
			<div class="install-label">Cursor</div>
			<code>"command": "npx",<br/>"args": ["-y", "football-docs"]</code>
		</div>
		<div class="install-card">
			<div class="install-label">VS Code / Copilot</div>
			<code>Add to .vscode/mcp.json</code>
		</div>
		<div class="install-card">
			<div class="install-label">Windsurf</div>
			<code>Add to mcp_config.json</code>
		</div>
		<div class="install-card">
			<div class="install-label">npm</div>
			<code>npx -y football-docs</code>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section-title">Tools</div>

	<div class="tools-row">
		<div class="tool-card">
			<div class="tool-name">search_docs</div>
			<div class="tool-desc">Full-text search across all providers</div>
		</div>
		<div class="tool-card">
			<div class="tool-name">list_providers</div>
			<div class="tool-desc">See all indexed providers</div>
		</div>
		<div class="tool-card">
			<div class="tool-name">compare_providers</div>
			<div class="tool-desc">Compare how providers handle concepts</div>
		</div>
		<div class="tool-card">
			<div class="tool-name">request_update</div>
			<div class="tool-desc">Flag outdated docs or request new ones</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section-title">Example queries</div>

	<ul class="example-queries">
		<li>"What is Opta qualifier 76?"</li>
		<li>"How does StatsBomb represent shots?"</li>
		<li>"Compare Opta and Wyscout coordinates"</li>
		<li>"Does SportMonks have xG?"</li>
		<li>"How does SPADL represent a tackle?"</li>
	</ul>

	<div class="section-title">Indexed providers</div>

	<div class="providers-grid">
		<div class="provider-chip"><div class="provider-name">StatsBomb</div><div class="provider-chunks">143 chunks</div></div>
		<div class="provider-chip"><div class="provider-name">kloppy</div><div class="provider-chunks">100 chunks</div></div>
		<div class="provider-chip"><div class="provider-name">SportMonks</div><div class="provider-chunks">71 chunks</div></div>
		<div class="provider-chip"><div class="provider-name">databallpy</div><div class="provider-chunks">63 chunks</div></div>
		<div class="provider-chip"><div class="provider-name">mplsoccer</div><div class="provider-chunks">62 chunks</div></div>
		<div class="provider-chip"><div class="provider-name">Wyscout</div><div class="provider-chunks">61 chunks</div></div>
		<div class="provider-chip"><div class="provider-name">Free sources</div><div class="provider-chunks">45 chunks</div></div>
		<div class="provider-chip"><div class="provider-name">soccerdata</div><div class="provider-chunks">40 chunks</div></div>
		<div class="provider-chip"><div class="provider-name">Opta</div><div class="provider-chunks">29 chunks</div></div>
		<div class="provider-chip"><div class="provider-name">socceraction</div><div class="provider-chunks">26 chunks</div></div>
	</div>

	<div class="cta-banner">
		<h2>Placeholder CTA headline</h2>
		<p>Placeholder description goes here.</p>
		<code>claude mcp add football-docs -- npx -y football-docs</code>
	</div>

	<div class="footer">
		<p>
			<a href="https://github.com/withqwerty/football-docs">GitHub</a> ·
			<a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/football-docs">npm</a> ·
			MIT License ·
			Made by <a href="https://github.com/withqwerty">withqwerty</a>
		</p>
	</div>
</ProductLayout>
